\mt1 1 TESARONAIKA 
\mt2 Khe Por Fharav TesaronaikaiŇč Ndi Khergi Gap 
\imt1 Khe fharav gan…®nga buni khare. 
\ip Tesaronaika, ana Masedonia Ňčgu bak…®me fhain ki Ňčgu bak…®me ma. Por Firipai thav, khavgia vov, Tesaronaika Ňčgu bak…®men vugap, ana maam sios mbe khavgi. Ndu Farasarigi Gumgi 17.1-9 Por maam sios khavgim, ZudaiŇč garim, gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve, mbe Por nzuai buni mbarav, guigira Zisas khoth…®gim, mbe ne nzuav Por ga nzuav ndavi simgiap, maaŇč Por ga mbuim, ana Tesaronaika thav, vugi. Por zumgum vov, Korin Ňčgu bak…®men kim, ana phorgap mba Ňčaara mbui guma Timoti, anan han vugap, ana mba Tesaronaikan kav guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigir h…®gi bigeŇč bun ana suaŇčgi. 
\ip Por mbaram Timoti suaŇčgi buni mbararagiap, Por gu Sairas, Timoti mbe wari t…®gap mbu Tesaronaikan kav, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi ndavi havhar…®r zav, kha gava khergi. Bigi kaŇčgi gumgi vh…®rve kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, kha Por khergi gavi, nta kha Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gavar ki, mbe kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, kha gap, ana Por fhara guarara khergi gap ma. Por kha gava kherav, ana Tesaronaikan kav, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, ana mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®var ndikndigap, ana vh…®ra mbe mbui t…®vir ndikndigi. 
\ip Mbe vh…®ra maaŇč kav, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe vh…®ra Zisas taagi zir…®rga tuav, mbe ana kaŇčgi fhuvara. Mbe vh…®ra khueŇč kaŇčgir za mbui, mba vh…®zgi gumgi, mbe Krais ntigar zir…®rga, mbe vh…®ra zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ndigirie? Mbe vh…®ra khaŇč nzuai, Krais maaŇčgi tugar zir…®rie? Mbe mba nzambari ga muuŇčgim, Por mben nzambari Ňčgarkarav khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde t…®vir vhuuiŇčra z…®n Ňčg…®p, nde Guma Bak…®me taagi zir…®rgeŇč suaŇčv anan rarg…® k…®ri.‚ÄĚ 
\c 1  
\ms1 Por wo phorga Ňčgari gumgir kov, mbe TesaronaikaiŇč kora muuŇčgi. 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt FG 17.1-13; 2 Te 1.1\x*Gu Por, Sairas, gu Timoti, nza kha gava khergiap, nde Tesaronaika Ňčgu bak…®men kav guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, nza anan nde ndi mbai. Nde nza Ndia Fhe Bak…®me gum Guma Bak…®me Zisas Krais phorga ki gumgi gu mbigi ma. 
\p Fhe Bak…®me nden korar muuŇčv, ndavi m…®…®t…®gir nden n…®…®Ňčrim, nde k…®ri. 
\s1 Por TesaronaikaiŇč guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®var ndikndigi. 
\p  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Ef 1.16; Fi 1.3-4; Kor 1.3; 2 Te 1.11\x*Nza zazera nde nd…®knd…®gap, nde nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav, ana ndikndigi. Nza zazera Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav, nza za nde z…®ri zitav Fhe Bak…®me nzuai.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt 1 Ko 13.13; Ga 5.6; Kor 1.4-6; Hi 6.10\x*Nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®k nde ndavi khavim, nde t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbuav, nde Ňčaarir vhuuiŇčra mbuav, wari won ndavi ndiv harigi gumgi ga nd…®…®i. Nde vh…®ra wari wo ndavi havhargiap, nza wo Bak…®me Zisas Krais taagia zir…®rga tugar rargap wari ki. Nza ne nzuav, nza wo Ndia Fhe Bak…®me phorga ndavar ana ndikndigi.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt 1 Ko 2.4-5; 4.20; Kor 2.2; 3.12; 2 Te 2.13; Hi 2.3\x*Nde nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, Fhe Bak…®me guigira wo ndarar nde n…®…®Ňčgim, nza vh…®ra guigira khueŇč kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me nden wora mbuigi. 
\p  
\v 5 Nza mba Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč ndiga nde ndi vugi, ne fura h…®gi buna kh…®neŇč fhuvara. Ne Fhe Bak…®men ŇčkasŇčka gum ana Ňäina Ňäaara phorga him, nde nza khaŇč t…®ga havhargiap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®v, nde guigira ana gangi. Nde vh…®ra, nde nduarira nza nden r…®gar kav nden kurkurigi t…®v, nde ana kangi. Nza nden kurkurar zav, ne muuŇčgi. 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt FG 17.1-9; 1 Ko 4.16; 11.1; Fi 3.17; 2 Te 3.9\x*Nde nzan t…®va ndigap, nde vh…®ra Guma Bak…®me t…®va ndigi. Nde Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč ndigim, simt…®gi vh…®rve nden hi. Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar nde ndavi khavim, nde ndikndigap, nde mba bunen ndigi.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt 1 Pi 5.3\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde t…®var vhuuŇčra mba Masedonia fhaiŇč gum Akaia fhain kav guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi kh…®vigi.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Ro 1.8\x*Nde Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč bun nzuaim, ne mbar vov, mbar vui, ne mbe ph…®…®aŇč mbuim, ana kh…®kh…®m mbar vui fara muuŇčgiap vui. Mba buna vhuueŇč Masedonia gum Akaia fhaiŇčra vui fhuvara. Mba buna vhuueŇč za mba fhain ki Ňčguir vuim, mbe za nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi kameŇč mbararagi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nza wom mbe suanga kameŇč ki fhu.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt FG 14.15; 1 Ko 12.2; Ga 4.8; 1 Te 2.1\x*Nza nden han zim, mbe nduarira mba hegi bigi, mbe nta bun nza nzuai. Mbe nde mbar…®vi gu tori thav, ndavi dorgap, nde zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki Fhe Bak…® guara z…®n vui, mbe ne bun nza nzuai. Mbe ne bun nzuav, vh…®ra nde Fhe Bak…®me Ňčaara gumgi kav,  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt FG 17.31; 1 Te 4.16; 5.9; Ta 2.13; 2 Pi 3.12\x*nde vh…®ra ana Kam Hevenan keg…®p taagi zir…®rganen rarga ki. Anan Kam rimgim, ana taagia ana khavgi. Ana Zisas ma, ana taagia nza ndi. Nza zumgum Fhe Bak…®men ndav shir…® h…®rga tugar, nza nzerara k…®rga. 
\c 2  
\s1 Por Tesaronaikan wo muuŇčgi Ňčaara nzuai. 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt 1 Te 1.5; 1.9\x*Nde na phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, nde nduarira gu nden r…®gar ka muuŇčgi Ňčaar, nde ana kaŇčgi, mba Ňčaara fhura vov vh…®zgi fhuvara.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt FG 16.19-24; 17.1-9; Fi 1.30; Kor 2.1\x*Nde kaŇčgi, nza ntigar nden han z…®rga, mba tugen nza Firipai Ňčgu bak…®men ki. Nza anan kav, nza zaa bak…®me ndim, mbe nzan fhavir farfav, nza mbevav, buni mbat…®gi nza nzuai. Nza ntigem nden han zegim, gumgi mbari nza mbevim, nzan Fhe Bak…®me, ana Ňčg…®r…®t…®n nza n…®…®Ňčgim, nza mba khesharigi farfar r…®vi fhu. Fhuvara. Nza khaŇč t…®gap th…®ga havhargiap, Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč bun nde nzuai.  
\v 3 Nza vh…®ra, nza guigira Zisas khoth…®g…®v, ana z…®n Ňčg…®r zav nde nzuav, nza pham buni tharir nde suaŇčgi fhu, nza vh…®ra t…®va mbat…®ga thuen nden muunga nd…®knd…®k the kav, nde vhagi fhu, nza vh…®ra t…®va thuen nde guigi fhu. Zak…®ra fhuvara!  
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Jer 11.20; Ga 1.10; 1 T 1.11\x*Fhe Bak…®me nzan mparav, ana nduara wo vuzvugara, ana won buna vhuueŇč bun suan zav, kha Ňčaarar nza n…®…®Ňčgi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nza kha gumgi gu mbigi nzan Ňčaara vuzvug…®r zav nza Fhe Bak…®men buna vhuueŇč bun nzuai fhu. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Fhe Bak…®me, ana nduara nzan ndavi vheri gari, ana nduara nzan Ňčaara vuzvug…®rga.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Zo 5.41; 5.44; FG 20.33; Ro 1.9; 1 Ko 9.1-6; 2 Ko 11.9; 1 Te 2.10; 2 Te 3.8-9; 2 Pi 2.3\x*Nde kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me vh…®ra nen nde suanga, nza nde raaŇč shi buna thuen nde nzuai fhuvara. Nza vh…®ra nde bigi gangiap, nta niihegap, kha buna vhuuen nde nzuai fhuvara.  
\v 6 Nza gumgi, nza z…®ri ndi vun kuamkuargeŇč vuzvugi fhu. Nza vh…®ra nde harigi gumgi gu mbigi, nza z…®ri ndi vun kuamkuargeŇč vuzvugi fhu.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt 1 Ko 2.3; 2 Ko 13.4; 2 T 2.24\x*KhueŇč guigira, nza Krais nzan farasarigim, nza ana Ňčaara gumgi ki. Nza maaŇč muuŇčgi vuzvuk kake, nza warir kurkurar zav simt…®gen nde nd…®…®e. Nza nde phorga ki tugen, nza mbarara nde phorga kav, mbarara nde phorga Ňčgari. Nza mbik tan won tara nd…®…®i fara muuŇčgiap kegi.  
\v 8 Nza guigira, wari wo ndavir nde n…®…®Ňčgiap, nza maaŇč muuŇčgiap Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč bun nde suan za mbui. Nza vh…®ra nden kurkurar zav, za wari won fhavi ndiv nde n…®…®Ňčgi. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, nde guigira nzan kaa gumgi guari ma. 
\p  
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt FG 20.34; 1 Ko 4.12; 2 Ko 11.9; 12.15\x*Nde nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, nza nde phorga kav, Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč bun nzuav, nza wari wo mba nzuav Ňčaara mbat…®ga muuŇčgi, nde ne kaŇčgi. Nza khaŇč t…®ga havhargiap, raa gu maan mba Ňčaara muuŇčgi. Nza khueŇč nzuav maaŇč muuŇčgi, nza mban wari gan…®ngeŇč suaŇčv simt…®gar nden n…®…®Ňč thagi. 
\p  
\v 10 Nde kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me vh…®ra, nen nden suanga, nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, nza nde muuŇčgi t…®vi, ana vh…®ra nta kaŇčgi. Nza Fhe Bak…®me n…®man, nza t…®vir Ňčaarira muuŇčgi. Nza t…®va mbat…®ga thuen nde muuŇčgi fhu. Nza vh…®ra gumgi nza s…®v, nza suanga t…®va mbat…®ga thuen nde muuŇčgi fhuvara.  
\v 11-12 \x - \xo 2:11-12 \xt FG 20.31\x*\x - \xo 2:11-12 \xt Fi 1.27; Kor 1.10; 2 T 1.9; 1 Pi 5.10\x*Nde kaŇčgi, nza ndia won tara mbui t…®vara nde muuŇčgi. Nza mba t…®var nde mbuav, nde nd…®knd…®gi khavav, nden ndavi havhari bunira nde suaŇčgi. Nza nde nzuav, nza Fhe Bak…®me guigira vuzvugi t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®r zav nde suaŇčgi. Fhe Bak…®me mba t…®vara z…®n Ňčg…®r zav nden kamgi. Mba t…®vara, nde Fhe Bak…®me wo gumgi gu mbigi garim, mbe ana piin ki, Ňčgu Hevenan Ňčgirg…®p, nde mpirmpir…®gar vhuun muuŇčgirga. 
\s1 Guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe guigira th…®ga havhargiap simt…®gi ndi. 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Ga 1.11-12; 4.14; 1 Te 1.2-3; 2 Te 2.13; 2 Pi 3.2\x*Nza vh…®ra zazera khueŇč nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav ana ndikndigi. Nde nza th…®…®ri t…®n Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč ndiav, nde guma won nd…®knd…®gar nzuai buni ndi t…®va muuŇčgiap ne ndigi fhuvara. Nde guigira Fhe Bak…®me buna guareŇč, nde ne khoth…®gap ne ndigi. Ne guigira Fhe Bak…®me buna guareŇč ma. Mba buneŇč, nde guigira Zisas Krais khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, mba buneŇč khaŇč t…®gap havhargiap, nde ndavi vherir Ňčgari.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt FG 17.5; Hi 10.33-34\x*Nde na phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, nde Zudian guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi fara muuŇčgi. Mbe Zisas Krais phorgi gumgi gu mbigi ma. Nden k…®vntogi simt…®gar nde nd…®…®i t…®vara, mbe Zudian kav guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, ZudaiŇč simt…®gar mbe n…®…®Ňčgi.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt FG 2.23; 3.15; 7.52; 9.23; 9.29; 13.45; 13.50; 14.2; 14.5; 14.19; 17.5; 17.13; 18.12\x*ZudaiŇč, mbe nza Bak…®me Zisas shogim, ana rimgim, mbe vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč gumgi, mbe vh…®ra mbe shogim, mbe vh…®zgi. Mbe vh…®ra nza vharvharigi. Mbe Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugi t…®vi, mbe nta dagasuav, panan za kha gumgi ga kegi.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16 \xt Mt 23.32-33; 24.6; Ru 11.52; FG 13.50\x*Mbe nza Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč bun harigi fhaiŇč gumgi ga suanga tuav, mbe ana mp…®ri. Mbe khueŇč nzuav, mbe Fhe Bak…®me taagip mba gumgi gu mbigi ndirganen, mbe suangane vuzvugi fhu. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap, zazera t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui. Mbe maaŇč mbuav simt…®gir warira phogi ga vuav, vov ntige mpuu bigeŇč ga muuŇčgi. Mbe maaŇč mbuim, Fhe Bak…®men ndav shir…® ntigera mben ki. 
\s1 Por guigira taagip TesaronaikaiŇč gan…®ngeŇč vuzvugi. 
\p  
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt 1 Te 3.10\x*Nde nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, kha ZudaiŇč nza mbuim, nza tuga t…®vaneŇčra nde thav, khar kav, nza kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, ndia won tari thav, samra ki. Nza nden Ňčkoo gari fhuvara, nzan nd…®knd…®gi gum nzan ndavi vheri nde phorga ki. Nza maaŇč muuŇčgiap taagi nde gan…® zav tuavi ndi garav Ňčaara mbat…®ga mbuav khar ki. Nza guigira nde gangirga vuzvuk bak…®me nzan ki.  
\v 18 Nza nden han Ňčg…®rgeŇč vuzvugi. Gu Por, gu tugi vh…®rvera, gu nden han Ňčg…®r za mbuim, Satan nzan tuav mp…®ri.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 2:19 \xt Fi 2.15-16; 4.1; 2 Te 1.4\x*Nza khaŇč muuŇčv k…®rga, nza Bak…®me Zisas taagip zir…®rga, thag…®na big…®n nzan muuŇčgirim, nza havhargip, ana n…®ma th…®g…®p ndikndig…®rie? Nza thag…®na big…®na ndigi Ňčg…®p, ana kh…®vav, khaŇč suaŇčrie, nza Ňčaara vhuuaŇč muuŇčgi? Nza ndera suaŇčv ndikndig…®rga.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 2:20 \xt 2 Ko 1.14; 1 Te 3.13; VB 1.7\x*AhaŇč, nza nden ndikndigi, nde nza muuŇčgim, nza ndavi nzerav ki. 
\c 3  
\s1 Por TesaronaikaiŇč havhar…® zav, Timoti ga sarigim, ana mben han vugi. 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt FG 17.15\x*Nza nde nd…®knd…®gi nd…®knd…®k guigira nzan k…®vgim, nza thav, kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, nza thag…®ne rarg…® k…®rie?  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt FG 16.1-3; Ef 3.13; 2 T 3.12\x*Nza mba nd…®knd…®ga muuŇčgiap, wari t…®gap, kama shogiap, Ňčka Atensan kav, Ňčka Timoti ga sarigim, ana nden han vugi. Timoti, ana nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi guma ma. Ana Fhe Bak…®men Ňčaara mbuav Zisas Krais buna vhuueŇč bun nzuai, guma ma. Nza ana sarigim, ana nden han Ňčg…®p, nden kurkurarim, nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®v havhargirga.  
\v 3 Nza khuen rivgi, nde mba simt…®gi gu zaagi ndiv, nde thari nd…®knd…®gi vh…®rve muunga. Nde nduarira kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me mba khesharigi simt…®gi ndir zav nzan farasarigi.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt FG 14.22; 20.24\x*Nza fhum nde phorga kav, nza khaŇč nde suaŇčgi, mbark…®rga simt…®gi nzan h…®rga. Nde tuituigip khueŇč kaŇčgiri, mba simt…®gi nzan h…®gi.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt Fi 2.16\x*Gu mba big…®na n…®…®reŇčra nzuav, gu thag…®ne rarg…® k…®rie? Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap Timoti ga sarigim, ana nden han vugi. Gu nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®va kaŇčgi zav ana sarigi. Gu khuen rivgi, nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi, nde muuŇčv k…®rim, Satan nden mp…®rarim, nza mba muuŇčgi Ňčaar, ana fhura mbar Ňčg…®g…®rga. 
\s1 Timoti Tesaronaikan vugap, kegap, taagiap kaman vhuueŇč ndiga Por ndi z…®gim, Por ne nzuav ndikndigi. 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt FG 18.5\x*Timoti nden han kegap, ana ntigera zav, nzan h…®gi. Ana h…®gap, kaman vhuuŇč guareŇčra nza n…®…®Ňčgi. Ana khaŇč nza nzuai, nde khaŇč t…®ga havhargiap, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi, nde guigira ndavir wari ga nd…®…®i. Ana vh…®ra khaŇč nzuai, nde zazera nza nd…®knd…®gap, nza nzuav ndavi mb…®rav ki. Nde, nza nde gangir zav, nde nd…®knd…®gap ndavi simgiap ki t…®vara muuŇčgiap, nde nza gangir zav ndavi simgiap ki.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt 2 Te 1.4\x*Nde nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, nza nde mbararagim, nde khaŇč t…®gap havhargiap, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi. Nza mba kameŇč mbararagiap, mba kameŇč nza ndavi havhargim, nzan hi simt…®gi gu zaagi, nza zam nta ndi.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Fi 4.1\x*Nza khueŇč kaŇčgi, nde maaŇč muuŇčgip havhargiap, Guma Bak…®me phorga kirga, nzan k…®r…® t…®vi guigira h…®gi.  
\v 9 Nza nde mbararagiap, nza wari wo Fhe Bak…®me n…®man, nza guigira ndikndiga bak…®me mbui. Nza ndikndigap, kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, nza Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav ana ndikndigi t…®v, ana nza n…®…®Ňčgi ndikndiga tukt…®gi fhuvara.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt FG 26.7; Ro 1.10; Kor 4.12; 2 T 1.3\x*Nza khaŇč t…®gap havhargiap, raari gu mbarir nza Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai, ana nza kh…®rarim, nza nde gan…® saŇčv mbar Ňčg…®rga. Nde maaŇč muuŇčgip guigira Zisas khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®k thaneŇč tivgirga, nza ana muuŇčgirim, ana havhargirga. 
\s1 Por Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai, ana ana sararim, ana mben han Ňčg…®rga. 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt 2 Te 2.16\x*Nza khueŇč vuzvugi, nzan Ndia Fhe Bak…®me gum nza Bak…®me Zisas, mani na suaŇčv tuavar muuŇčgirim, nza nden han Ňčg…®rga.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt 1 Te 4.9-10; 5.15; 2 Pi 1.7\x*Nza khueŇč vuzvugi, Guma Bak…®me nden muuŇčgirim, nde guigira wari won ndavir harigi gumgir n…®…®nga t…®v guigira nden k…®rga. Nde zam wari wo ndavi ndiv, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigir n…®…®Ňčv, vh…®ra za mba gumgi gu mbigir n…®…®nga. Nza wari won ndavir nde nd…®…®i t…®var, nde mben muuŇčri.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Sek 14.5; 1 Ko 1.8; Fi 1.10; 2 Te 1.7; 1.10; 2.17\x*Nde mba t…®vara muunga, Fhe Bak…®me nde ndavi havhargirga. Ana nde ndavi havhargirim, nde k…®rim, nza Bak…®me Zisas taagi won gumgi gu mbigir kov zir…®rga, ana nde gan…®rim, nde Ňčgaravra k…®rga. Nde vh…®ra nzerara k…®v, nde nza wo Ndia Fhe Bak…®me n…®man big…®na mbat…®ga thueŇč muuŇčgi ne suaŇčv kama thueŇč k…®rga fhu. Ne guigi guarara. 
\c 4  
\ms1 Mbe TesaronaikaiŇč, mbe Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugi t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®rim, mba t…®vi guigira mben k…®ri. 
\s1 Nza ruarir gumgi gu mbigi wari ndirga fhu. 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt Fi 1.27; Kor 1.10; 2.6; 1 Te 2.12; 2 Te 3.6\x*Nde nza wo Bak…®me Zisas z…®n panan nde suaŇčgi buni, nde nta kaŇčgi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, gu ntigem kha gavar khaŇč nde nzuai. Nza nde Fhe Bak…®me ndikndigirga t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®rga t…®vi, nza zam ntan nde kh…®vigi.  
\v 2 Nde mba t…®vi z…®n vui. Nza ntigem, guigira nde ndavi havhara nde nzuai. Nza wo Bak…®me Zisas z…®n panan khaŇč nde nzuai, nde mba t…®v, nde khaŇč t…®g…® havhargip, anan muuŇčv Ňčg…®ri.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 4:3 \xt 1 Ko 6.15; 6.18; Ef 5.3; 5.17; 5.27; Kor 3.5; 1 Te 5.23; Hi 10.10; 1 Pi 1.16\x*Fhe Bak…®me vuzvuk khaŇč muuŇčgi. Nde guigira zam wari won ndavir ana n…®…®Ňčgip, nde ana n…®man Ňčgaravra k…®ri. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde gumgi gu mbigi ruarir wari ndi t…®vi, nde guigira nta Ňčk…®…®ari.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 4:4 \xt Ro 6.19; 1 Ko 6.13-15; 6.18\x*Nde won ndavi vheri khavi vuzvugi mbat…®gi, nde nta gan…®ri, nta nde gan…® thari. Nde nta gan…®v, nde Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugi t…®vir muuŇčv, nde ana n…®man Ňčgaravra k…®v, nde vh…®ra harigi gumgi n…®man nzerara k…®ri. \f a \fr 4:4 \ft Kha Ňčanen mbe Grikar kaman suaŇčgi kameŇč tuituigiap h…®gi fhuvara. \f* 
\v 5 \x - \xo 4:5 \xt Sng 79.6; Ga 4.8; Ef 2.12; 4.17-18; 2 Te 1.8\x*Nde muuŇčv k…®rim, mba vuzvugi mbat…®gi gum nd…®knd…®gi mbat…®gi nde Ňčg…®rg…®rim, nde k…®r Fhe Bak…®me segi gumgi gu mbigi fara muuŇčgirga, mbe Fhe Bak…®me kaŇčgi fhu. Nde mbe farar muuŇčgip, mbark…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gir muuŇčv, vh…®ra ferfer…®p, ruarir gumgi gu mbigi wari ndirga.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 4:6 \xt Wkp 19.11-13; Sng 94.1; 1 Ko 6.8; 2 Te 1.8\x*Nde wari t…®gap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, nde mba t…®vi mbat…®gir mben muuŇčv, mbe guiguigip, mba t…®vir mben muuin muuŇč thari. Nza fhum kama havharar khaŇč nde suaŇčgi, Guma Bak…®me mba khesharigi t…®vi ga mbui gumgi, ana muumbara mbat…®gar mben muuŇčgirga.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 4:7 \xt 1 Ko 1.2; 2 Te 2.13-14; Hi 12.14; 1 Pi 1.14-16\x*Fhe Bak…®me mba khesharigi t…®vi mbat…®gir muun zav nzan kamgi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Ana t…®vir Ňčaarir muun zav nzan kamgi.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 4:8 \xt Ese 36.27; 37.14; Ru 10.16; 1 Ko 2.10; 2 Ko 1.22; 1 Zo 3.24\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, guma ana kha kameŇč daaŇčgia kh…®ngi, ana guma suaŇčgi kameŇčra daai fhuvara. Ana Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi kameŇč daasui. Mba Fhe Bak…®me, ana won Ňäina Ňäaarar nde nd…®…®i. 
\s1 Nza khaŇč t…®g…® havhargip, t…®vir vhuuin muuŇčri. 
\p  
\v 9 \x - \xo 4:9 \xt Zo 13.34; 15.12; Hi 8.11; 1 Zo 2.20; 2.27; 3.11-13\x*Gu nde ndavir guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigir n…®…®n saŇčv kama thueŇč kher…®v nde suanga fhu. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me nduara mba t…®var nde kh…®vigi.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 4:10 \xt 2 Te 3.4\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde wari won ndavir Masedonian fhain kav guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi ga nd…®…®i. Nde na phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, gu nde ndavi havhar…® za mbui. Nde khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, mba t…®var muuŇčv Ňčg…®ri.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 4:11 \xt Ef 4.28; 2 Te 3.8; 3.12; 1 Pi 4.15\x*Nde maaŇč muuŇčv, mbarara piigip, wari won Ňčaarir muuŇčri. Nde wari wo harira Ňčgar…®v, nduarira wari gan…®ri. Nza fhum mba kameŇč nde suaŇčgi.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt Ro 13.13; 2 Ko 8.21; Kor 4.5\x*Nde maaŇč muunga, nde big…®n the suaŇčv tivgirga fhu. Mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi fhu, mbe nden t…®vir ndikndig…®rga. 
\s1 Guma Bak…®me taagi zir…®v nza fug…®rga. 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 4:13 \xt Ef 2.12\x*Nde nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, nza khueŇč vuzvugi, nde mba vh…®zgi gumgi gu mbigir h…®rga bigeŇč, nde ne kaŇčgirga. Nde ne kaŇčgirga fhuv, nde pim vh…®zi gumgi ga suaŇčv nziv k…®rga. Nde mba Zisas khoth…®gi fhuv gumgi gu mbigi farar muuŇčgirga. Mbe Fhe Bak…®me taagip mba vh…®zgi gumgi gu mbigi khav…®rga, mbe nen rarga ki fhuvara.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 4:14 \xt Ro 14.9; 1 Ko 15.3-4; 15.12-13; 15.18; 15.23\x*Nza khueŇč khoth…®gi, Zisas rimgiap, taagia khavgi, ana taagip zir…®rga. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nza vh…®ra khueŇč khoth…®gi, mba guigira Zisas khoth…®gap vh…®zgi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe vh…®ra taagi khavgirga. Fhe Bak…®me taagi mbe ndigirim, mbe Zisas phorg…®p anan han naanga. 
\p  
\v 15 \x - \xo 4:15 \xt 1 Ko 15.51-52\x*Nza Guma Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nde nzuav, nza khaŇč nzuai. Guma Bak…®me taagi zir…®rga, nza ntige khaŇč Ňčamki gumgi gu mbigi, nza mba vh…®zgi gumgi gu mbigi kambarav fhararga tukt…®gi fhu. Fhuvara!  
\v 16 \x - \xo 4:16 \xt Mt 24.30-31; FG 1.11; 1 Ko 15.23; 15.52; 1 Te 1.10; 2 Te 1.7\x*Fhe Bak…®me khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip suanga, anan enserar vhari kam…®nga, Fhe Bak…®men mbar…®p s…®m…®nga, Guma Bak…®me Hevenan keg…®p, zir…®rga. Mba guigira Zisas khoth…®gap vh…®zgi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe fharav khavgirga.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 4:17 \xt Zo 12.26; FG 1.9; VB 11.12\x*Nza mba tugen, nza guigira Zisas khoth…®gap Ňčamki gumgi gu mbigi, nza mbe phorg…®p, nza zam naaŇčv, buivar Guma Bak…®men purga. Nza ana han ndav, nza zazera Guma Bak…®me phorg…®p mbara muuŇčgip k…®rga.  
\v 18 Nde kha buni bun wari ga suaŇčv, wari ndavi havhar…®ri. 
\c 5  
\s1 Nza wari th…®th…®m t…®g…®p, Guma Bak…®me zir…®rga tugar rarg…®p k…®rga. 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 5:1 \xt Mt 24.36\x*Nde nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, nza mba bigi h…®rga raa gum tuga bun nde suaŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 5:2 \xt Mt 24.42-44; Ru 12.39; 2 Pi 3.10; VB 3.3\x*Nde nduarira kaŇčgi, Guma Bak…®me zir…®rga tuk, ana k…®…®i guma maan k…®m…®n zav zi fara muuŇčgi.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 5:3 \xt Ese 13.10; Hos 13.13; Mt 24.39; Ru 21.34-35; Zo 16.21-22\x*Mba gumgi gu mbigi khaŇč suanga, ‚ÄúNtige tugar vhuuŇč ma, nza nzerara ki.‚ÄĚ Mbe maaŇč suanga, mben farfarga big…®n, ana vhemkora mben h…®g…®rga, mba big…®na zaa mbik tara t…®r zav zaa ndi zaa farar muuŇčgip mben h…®g…®rga. Mbe mba big…®na Ňčk…®…®arga tukt…®gi fhuvara.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 5:4 \xt Ro 13.12-13; 1 Zo 2.8\x*Nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, nde g…®ng…®nan ki fhuvara. Nde g…®ng…®nan k…®v, nde mba tuk nden h…®rim, nde guma k…®ma guma garim, ana hanera ana him, ana Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgi farar muuŇčrie? Fhuvara!  
\v 5 \x - \xo 5:5 \xt Ro 13.12; Ef 5.8-9\x*Nde zam vhava Ňčarar kav, nde raar ki fara muuŇčgiap ki nt…®…®ri ma. Nza maaŇč gum g…®ng…®nan ki nt…®…®ri fhuvara.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 5:6 \xt Mt 24.42; 25.5; 25.13; 1 Pi 5.8\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nza muuŇčv k…®v, nza harigi gumgi farar muuŇčgip kuv k…®rga. Fhuvara! Nza semsegip wari ga nzuav gan…®v k…®rga.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 5:7 \xt Ru 21.34-36; Ro 13.13; Ef 5.14\x*Nza kaŇčgi, kui gumgi, mbe maan kui. Phara ŇčanŇčari pi gumgi, mbe maan nta pi.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 5:8 \xt Ais 59.17; Ef 6.13-17\x*Nza m…®n thugim, nza raar ki gumgi, nza nd…®knd…®gi bigi kaŇčgip wari gan…®v k…®rga. Nza vh…®ra guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®va ndigip, ana z…®n Ňčg…®p, guigira won ndavi ndi harigi gumgi gu mbigi n…®…®Ňčri. Mba t…®v, nza siot kapa shari t…®var muuŇčgip, ana sh…®rari. Ana nden fhavi gan…®rim, nde nzerara k…®rga. Nza ana sharav, nza Fhe Bak…®me taagip nza ndirganen rarg…® k…®rga t…®v, nza kapa khorar fi t…®var muuŇčgip, ana fav k…®rga. Mba nd…®knd…®k, ana nza panan k…®v, nza nd…®knd…®gi gan…®nga. Nza maaŇč muuŇčgip tuituigip th…®g…® havhargip, wari gan…® k…®rga.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 5:9 \xt Ro 9.22; 1 Te 1.10; 2 Te 2.13-14; 1 Pi 2.8\x*Fhe Bak…®me won ndav shir…® ndir zav nza farasarigi fhuvara. Ana nza Guma Bak…®me Zisas Krais taagi nza ndir zav, ana nza farasarigi.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 5:10 \xt Ro 14.8-9; 2 Ko 5.15; 1 Te 4.14\x*Zisas nzan kurkurar zav rimgi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nza Ňčamki o, nza rimgi, nza zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ndigip ana phorg…® k…®rga.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 5:11 \xt Zu 1.20\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde bevbevira nde bunin vhuuiŇčra guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi phorg…®v suaŇčv, mbe ndavi havhar…®ri. Nde ntige mba t…®va mbui, nde mba t…®vara muuŇčri. 
\s1 Fhe Bak…®me guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigir kurkurarim, mbe t…®vir vhuuiŇčra muunga. 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 5:12 \xt 1 Ko 16.18; Fi 2.29; 1 T 5.17; Hi 13.7; 13.17\x*Nde nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, nza khueŇč vuzvugi. Nden kurkurigi gumgi, nde mben piin k…®ri. Guma Bak…®me mbe ndi fegim, mbe nde gari gumgir pani ki. Mbe kav Ňčaara mbat…®ga mbuav bunin nde nzuav nden t…®vi ndiv th…®gar mbai.  
\v 13 Nde mbe mbui Ňčaara nd…®knd…®g…®p, ndavi mb…®rav guigira mben piin k…®v guigira wari won ndavi mben n…®…®Ňčri. Nde mbe vuzvug…®p, nde vh…®ra wari t…®g…®p ndava bavira k…®ri. 
\p  
\v 14 \x - \xo 5:14 \xt Ga 5.22; 6.1-2; Kor 3.12; 2 Te 3.6; 3.11; 3.15; Hi 12.12\x*Nde nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, nza mba vhukvhugi gumgir t…®vi ndi th…®gar maan zav, nde nd…®knd…®gi khavav, vh…®ra r…®vi gumgi ndavi havhar…®v, mba th…®ga havhargi fhuv gumgi, nza mben kurkura zav nde nzuai. Nde mbarara mba gumgi ga suaŇčri. 
\p  
\v 15 \x - \xo 5:15 \xt Snd 20.22; Mt 5.39; Ro 12.17; 1 Ko 6.7; 1 Pi 3.9\x*Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgip t…®vi mbat…®gir nde muuŇčrim, nde mbe mbui t…®vi mbat…®gi Ňčgarka thari. Nde zazera khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, warir kurkurav, zam mba gumgi gu mbigir kurkurari. 
\p  
\v 16-17 \x - \xo 5:16-17 \xt 2 Ko 6.10; Fi 4.4\x*\x - \xo 5:16-17 \xt Ru 18.1; Ef 6.18; Kor 4.2; 1 Pi 4.7\x*Nde zazera ndikndig…®p, zazera Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®p suaŇčri.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 5:18 \xt Ef 5.20; Kor 3.17\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, big…®n thueŇč nden h…®g…®rim, nde ne suaŇčv sim…® thari, nde ne suaŇčv Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®p suaŇčv, nen ndikndig…®ri. Fhe Bak…®me khueŇč vuzvugi, nde Krais Zisas phorga havhargi gumgi gu mbigi, nde mba t…®var muuŇčri. 
\p  
\v 19 \x - \xo 5:19 \xt Ef 4.30; 1 T 4.14; 2 T 1.6\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar big…®n thuen muun saŇčv nde nd…®knd…®gi khav…®rim, nde ana mbev…® thari.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 5:20 \xt 1 Ko 14.1; 14.39\x*Nde guma Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč guma buni nzuai mbugum buni suaŇčrim, nde khaŇč suaŇč thari, ne fhura ki buneŇč ma.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 5:21 \xt 1 Ko 2.11; 2.15; Fi 4.8; 1 Zo 4.1\x*Nde tuituigip ana nzuai buni mbararav, nta nd…®knd…®g…®ri, nta guigira Fhe Bak…®me buni guari o, nta harigi guma nd…®knd…®gar nzuai buni. Nde t…®vir vhuuiŇč, nde nta suirari.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 5:22 \xt Jop 1.1; 1.8; 2.3\x*Nde nta suirav, mbark…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gi, nde nta Ňčk…®…®ari. 
\p  
\v 23 \x - \xo 5:23 \xt Ro 15.33; 1 Ko 1.8; Fi 4.9; 1 Te 3.13; 2 Te 3.16\x*Fhe Bak…®me, ana ndava m…®…®t…®gar n…®…®Ňčge ma. Ana nden muuŇčgirim, nde guigira wari wo ndavir zam ana n…®…®Ňčgirga, ana nden muuŇčgirim, nde guigira Ňčgararga. Ana nden vherir ki gumgi, nden ntuu, nden fhavi, ana nta gan…®nga, guma big…®n thueŇč suaŇčv fharar nde s…®rga fhu, nde za nzerara k…®rga. Nde nzerara k…®rim, nza Bak…®me Zisas Krais taagi zir…®rga tuk h…®g…®rga.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 5:24 \xt 1 Ko 1.9; 10.13; 2 Te 3.3\x*Fhe Bak…®me nden kamgi, ana mba t…®vir nden muunga. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, ana wo nzuai buni, ana zam nta z…®n vui. 
\p  
\v 25 \x - \xo 5:25 \xt Kor 4.3; 2 Te 3.1\x*Nde nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, nde nza suaŇčv Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®v suaŇčrim, ana nzan kurkurarga. 
\p  
\v 26 \x - \xo 5:26 \xt Ro 16.16\x*Nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, nza won t…®v nde bevbevira, nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgir harir suig…®p, mbe viav…®ri. 
\p  
\v 27 Gu guma Bak…®me z…®n kaman havharar nde nzuai, nde kha gava gan…®v za nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčri. 
\p  
\v 28 Nza Bak…®me Zisas Kraisan kora muumbar nde phorg…® k…®ri.